# urirun-connector-cron

`cron://` — manage cron entries, a calendar of upcoming runs, and export schedules to
iCalendar (`.ics`) / Google CSV for import on any platform. Only lines tagged
`# urirun:<id>` are touched; the rest of your crontab is preserved.
